<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM2.1">
<l>tēṭṭaruntiṟaṟ ṟēṉiṉaitteṉ ṉaraṅkaṉaittiru mātuvāḻ</l>
<l>vāṭṭamilvaṉa mālaimārvaṉai vāḻttimālkoṭcin taiyarā</l>
<l>āṭṭamēvi yalantaḻaittayar veytumeyyaṭi yārkaḷtam</l>
<l>īṭṭaṅkaṇṭiṭak kūṭumēlatu kāṇuṅkaṇpaya ṉāvatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [one] gets to see the throng of true servants who praise</l>
<l rend="indent">the hard-to-seek, vigour[-giving] Honey, Him from Raṅgam in the South,</l>
<l rend="indent">Him with a chest [bedecked with] unwithering sylvan garlands</l>
<l rend="indent">where Śrī lives,</l>
<l>who, with [their] minds suffering from confusion,</l>
<l>join the dance, get distressed, call [Him],</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] attain forgetfulness,</l>
<l>that is the purpose of eyes that [can] see.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
